description: kneat.com, inc. designs, develops, and supplies software for data and document management within regulated environments in the United States, Ireland, Canada, and internationally. The company offers Kneat Gx platform, a configurable commercial off-the-shelf application focused on validation lifecycle management and testing for biotechnology, pharmaceutical, and medical device manufacturing industries. Its platform is used in process, computer system, cleaning, analytical instrument, method, utility and facility, equipment, and cold chain validation, as well commissioning and qualification, and electronic logbook management. The company also provides software-related services, including training, installation, upgradation, consulting, and maintenance, as well as process mapping, project management, and other services. kneat.com, inc. is headquartered in Limerick, Ireland.
